{"tid":1696992,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加大熱教拜仁","createTime":"2019-11-06T14:19:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T14:54:29.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"96f471fd22cb07e43b8e9a99206d5b190f315a9c","tid":1696992,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T14:19:30.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】德甲班霸拜仁慕尼黑新帥備受關注，前阿仙奴領隊雲加領軍賠率升溫，成頂頭大熱。<br />\n<br />\n拜仁慕尼黑不敵法蘭克福後，辭退尼高高華，並聲稱將會花3星期尋覓真命天子，暫由菲力克領軍。現年70歲的雲加（Arsene Wenger）成繼任大熱。根據外國博彩公司顯示，2017/18年球季離開兵工廠的雲加，現時以1.5倍升上榜首，前曼聯領隊摩連奴則以6倍排名次席。<br />\n<br />\n前祖雲達斯教練柯歷利排名第3，為8倍，而阿積士主帥坦哈格則以11倍成為黑馬。<br />\n<br />\n早前被問到有沒有興趣接掌拜仁，雲加直認不諱：「當然有，執教是一生的工作，每個人的答案都一樣，你會掛念那些東西。」拜仁易帥前，聯賽跌至第4位，落後榜首4分，周三歐聯主場對奧林比亞高斯。"},{"pid":"11e7def20d9d3efeb0026565c4ced2c4a0dd3987","tid":1696992,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T14:20:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/TLlm0bgreA8/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FTLlm0bgreA8%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=6a355fc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雲加城府深到 為教拜仁佯裝大敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb9f05e7d0ff8580b829131b38d4a02a6d742984","tid":1696992,"uid":95489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11e7def20d9d3efeb0026565c4ced2c4a0dd3987","tid":1696992,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T14:20:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/TLlm0bgreA8/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FTLlm0bgreA8%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=6a355fc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雲加城府深到 為教拜仁佯裝大敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T14:54:29.000Z","msg":"黑暗兵法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n爺爺大敗係為未來去拜為未來鋪路"}]}